{"tid":552880,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"禁區上落客上訴上庭","createTime":"2018-02-07T03:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T19:26:24.000Z","uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1ffc0a80a87bd9b40b05929901c78ade21624aec","tid":552880,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"都知道交450了左件事係唔駛煩。<br />\n<br />\n但如果上庭，有冇人試過成功上訴?<br />\n如果得一個差佬目擊，還要是距離好遠(唔係十米內)，條街又多人，有看錯嘅機會，又冇影片和相做證，得個講字;<br />\n上到庭是否只是口同鼻呦?跟本冇有力證據證明?<br />\n再加上懷疑自己撞到野或機件故障，無論係咪禁區都有責任落車睇睇掛?唔係真係有意外走左去咪仲大單?"},{"pid":"1f10ffd4ec7c240a730b283d82300aca93866958","tid":552880,"uid":136640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"禁區停一陣 唔會有差佬搞你 但上落客斷正就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c137228e6f7a6f71bdc617c2450f7531c979a37","tid":552880,"uid":30058,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"依你咁講全部票都唔使交啦<br />\n都係得一個差佬同你口同鼻拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57401ce673415add1ade582dc468fdd656b4134","tid":552880,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"我諗你要有好有力嘅證據證明捉你嗰位當時判斷有問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5533afda1cb8aa869f1361c93ee5569743ccec25","tid":552880,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"c57401ce673415add1ade582dc468fdd656b4134","tid":552880,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"我諗你要有好有力嘅證據證明捉你嗰位當時判斷有問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"既然大家都冇力證據，疑點利益歸於被告喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"